00:15:00,691 --> 00:15:02,026
Sempurna.

240
00:15:02,109 --> 00:15:02,943
Okey tak?

241
00:15:05,321 --> 00:15:06,614
Mestilah!

242
00:15:08,782 --> 00:15:11,035
Apa masalah yang mungkin ada?

243
00:15:11,118 --> 00:15:13,495
Carilah di seluruh bandar,

244
00:15:13,579 --> 00:15:18,334
tapi awak takkan jumpa tempat
dengan harga dan kemudahan begini.

245
00:15:18,417 --> 00:15:22,630
Ada rasa yang tak menyenangkan
di rumah ini.

246
00:15:26,926 --> 00:15:27,760
Saya terima.

247
00:15:28,802 --> 00:15:30,471
Saya akan sain dan pindah hari ini.

248
00:15:33,599 --> 00:15:35,726
Selamat datang ke dunia kegelapan.

249
00:15:37,937 --> 00:15:40,356
Mari kita pergi sain kontrak itu.

250
00:15:40,439 --> 00:15:42,441
Abaikan dia.

251
00:15:42,524 --> 00:15:44,693
Isteri dia pukul dia, jadi dia tak betul.

252
00:15:45,653 --> 00:15:48,405
Mari pergi, okey? Jom sain. Ayuh.

253
00:15:51,659 --> 00:15:52,785
Helo, kesayanganku!

254
00:15:52,868 --> 00:15:55,329
Ini Do Ga-yeong,
