PEMERHATI: OK-HUI
NEPOTISME

368
00:24:42,230 --> 00:24:43,064
{\an8}CANTIK TAPI DUNGU

369
00:24:43,148 --> 00:24:45,400
{\an8}"BUNGA SEPERTIKU!"
