00:25:07,088 --> 00:25:07,964
{\an8}STAMINA MAKSIMA

383
00:25:08,048 --> 00:25:10,383
{\an8}MESEJ STATUS: BUKAN PENGGUNA
JANGAN TANYA UMUR

