00:26:54,904 --> 00:26:56,448
Lihat betapa gelap doktor ini

424
00:26:56,531 --> 00:26:57,949
Inilah makna kegelapan.

425
00:26:58,033 --> 00:26:59,326
Saya rasa sama!

426
00:27:02,829 --> 00:27:06,041
Won, cuti dua tahun
dan pulihkan diri di suatu tempat.

427
00:27:09,794 --> 00:27:10,628
Di mana?

428
00:27:11,838 --> 00:27:14,382
Di tempat angin segar dan air yang jernih.

429
00:27:14,466 --> 00:27:16,426
Hawaii? Itali?

430
00:27:17,302 --> 00:27:18,303
Di mana?

431
00:27:19,512 --> 00:27:20,805
Ada satu tempat…

432
00:27:21,723 --> 00:27:23,266
Ia dipanggil Dongdu-dong.

433
00:27:24,225 --> 00:27:25,060
Donghae?

434
00:27:25,143 --> 00:27:27,771
Kenapa saya nak pergi ke Donghae?

435
00:27:27,854 --> 00:27:28,938
Bukan.

436
00:27:29,647 --> 00:27:31,524
Dongdu-dong.

437
00:27:31,608 --> 00:27:33,151
Di mana tempatnya?

438
00:27:33,234 --> 00:27:35,236
PEJABAT PENDAKWA DAERAH SEOHAN

439
00:27:48,208 --> 00:27:50,668
Apa sedang berlaku? Kenapa dengan mereka?

440
00:27:51,711 --> 00:27:54,589
Selepas tiga minggu
latihan asas ketenteraan,

441
