00:33:15,118 --> 00:33:16,119
Hei, mak.

499
00:33:16,703 --> 00:33:18,329
Kenapa dengan suara kamu?

500
00:33:19,497 --> 00:33:20,707
Saya tengah kerja.

501
00:33:21,749 --> 00:33:22,917
Kenapa mak telefon?

502
00:33:23,668 --> 00:33:25,253
Ada lelaki mencari kamu.

503
00:33:25,336 --> 00:33:27,630
Lelaki? Untuk apa?

504
00:33:28,506 --> 00:33:30,591
Maaf. Siapa nama awak?

505
00:33:31,968 --> 00:33:32,885
Gye Ji-ung.

506
00:33:33,886 --> 00:33:34,804
Dia ke sana?

507
00:33:34,887 --> 00:33:36,305
Gila betul!

508
00:33:42,854 --> 00:33:43,896
Maafkan saya!

509
00:33:47,233 --> 00:33:48,651
Apa? Tunggu.

510
00:33:48,735 --> 00:33:50,445
Bukankah itu Sun?

511
00:33:50,528 --> 00:33:51,696
Betul. Itu dia.

512
00:33:51,779 --> 00:33:54,323
Itu warna kot yang sama
dia pakai pergi kerja.

513
00:33:54,407 --> 00:33:55,992
Rambut yang sama panjang.

514
00:33:56,075 --> 00:33:58,870
Beg galas yang dia selalu bawa juga.

515
00:33:58,953 --> 00:34:00,538
Aduhai, lihat staminanya.

516
00:34:00,621 --> 00:34:02,832
Dia tunggang basikal
pergi dan balik kerja.

517
00:34:02,915 --> 00:34:04,625
Maaf, Ok-hui.

518
00:34:05,209 --> 00:34:07,295
Saya terpaksa mandi.

519
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:10,757
Apa kita nak buat?

520
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:13,885
Lim Sun ada hal mustahak
dan tiba-tiba pergi.

521
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:17,847
Kita kena tangguh
pertemuan sosial hari ini ke hari lain.

522
00:34:17,930 --> 00:34:18,931
Baiklah…

523
00:34:19,849 --> 00:34:21,726
- Pergi dulu.
- Apa?

524
00:34:22,852 --> 00:34:24,771
Aduhai, itu yang terbaik.

525
00:34:24,854 --> 00:34:27,023
Sekarang, lupakan wanita itu.

526
00:34:27,106 --> 00:34:28,733
Jom minum bersama.

527
00:34:28,816 --> 00:34:30,026
Saya nak pulang.

528
00:34:30,109 --> 00:34:31,986
Bukankah awak kata nak makan?

529
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:33,154
Kamu berdua pergi.

530
00:34:34,030 --> 00:34:36,407
Saya okey.

531
00:34:36,908 --> 00:34:39,243
- Nak ke mana?
- Betullah.

532
00:34:39,327 --> 00:34:42,955
Sesetengah orang tak faham-faham.

533
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:45,708
Sangat menjengkelkan.

534
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:59,388
<i>Ayah, syabas untuk hari ini.</i>

535
00:34:59,472 --> 00:35:01,933
<i>Ayah nak saya jemput ayah selepas makan?</i>

536
00:35:02,016 --> 00:35:03,101
<i>Ayah cuma gembira</i>

537
00:35:03,184 --> 00:35:06,562
<i>diberi peluang bekerja begini.</i>

538
00:35:07,313 --> 00:35:10,149
<i>Kamu tak perlu jemput ayah.</i>

539
00:35:10,983 --> 00:35:12,235
<i>Makan malam batal.</i>

540
00:35:12,860 --> 00:35:13,986
<i>Semasa pulang,</i>

541
00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:15,696
<i>ayah akan belikan makanan.</i>

542
00:35:42,348 --> 00:35:44,892
Bagaimana awak kenal anak saya?

543
00:35:46,936 --> 00:35:49,230
<i>Kami jumpa semasa saya</i>
<i>nak ke mesyuarat kerja.</i>

544
00:35:49,313 --> 00:35:50,439
<i>Kerja?</i>

545
00:35:50,523 --> 00:35:51,607
Awak kerja di pejabat?

546
00:35:53,442 --> 00:35:54,277
Penjawat awam.

547
00:35:54,986 --> 00:35:55,820
Penjawat awam?

548
00:35:57,613 --> 00:36:00,116
Aduhai, jadi awak penjawat awam!

549
00:36:00,199 --> 00:36:01,617
Baguslah!

550
00:36:02,243 --> 00:36:03,077
Sebentar.

551
00:36:03,661 --> 00:36:05,037
Tunggu. Mana adab saya?

552
00:36:20,595 --> 00:36:21,596
Apa itu?

553
00:36:21,679 --> 00:36:22,680
Lihat itu!

554
00:36:22,763 --> 00:36:23,723
Wah, hebatnya!

555
00:36:23,806 --> 00:36:24,849
Lihat itu!

556
00:36:24,932 --> 00:36:26,475
Hei, puan!

557
00:36:26,559 --> 00:36:28,311
Saya tak percaya wanita itu!

558
00:36:28,394 --> 00:36:30,354
- Hei, puan!
- Ayuh!

559
00:36:30,438 --> 00:36:32,440
<i>Anak saya juga penjawat awam.</i>

560
00:36:33,774 --> 00:36:34,817
Dia dah kerja?

561
00:36:34,901 --> 00:36:36,319
Apa maksud awak "dah"?

562
00:36:36,402 --> 00:36:37,862
Dia dapat masuk usia 30 tahun.

563
00:36:38,905 --> 00:36:42,742
Apa pun, kerjanya menjaminkan
dan dia boleh kerja sampai bersara.

564
00:36:56,631 --> 00:36:58,633
Boleh tanya tentang ibu bapa awak?

565
00:36:59,675 --> 00:37:00,801
Mereka tiada.

566
00:37:03,554 --> 00:37:05,556
Tapi jika mereka ada,

567
00:37:05,640 --> 00:37:08,267
mungkin ada konflik
antara isteri awak dan mentuanya.

568
00:37:08,351 --> 00:37:11,229
Sebaliknya, bahagia bersama dalam cinta

569
00:37:11,312 --> 00:37:13,064
adalah yang terbaik.

570
00:37:13,648 --> 00:37:14,649
Apa pendapat awak?

571
00:37:19,403 --> 00:37:20,738
Mana dia?

572
00:37:21,781 --> 00:37:23,491
Dia kata nak pulang selepas kerja.

573
00:37:25,409 --> 00:37:26,410
Apa pun,

574
00:37:26,869 --> 00:37:28,496
awak sangat tampan. Maksud saya…

575
00:37:28,579 --> 00:37:30,831
Urusan apa awak ada dengan Mi-jin?

576
00:37:31,499 --> 00:37:34,502
Awak bekerja di jabatan mana?

577
00:37:35,127 --> 00:37:36,128
Saya…

578
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:42,260
Apa wanita itu buat di sini?

579
00:37:43,844 --> 00:37:44,887
Puan!

580
00:37:52,311 --> 00:37:54,230
Bukan dia?

581
00:38:13,332 --> 00:38:14,375
Aduhai!

582
00:38:22,216 --> 00:38:23,092
Tak guna.

583
00:38:23,509 --> 00:38:26,053
Biar betul!

584
00:38:26,137 --> 00:38:29,348
Awak akan tahu betapa bijaknya Mi-jin
setelah kenal dia.

585
00:38:29,432 --> 00:38:30,266
Aduhai.

586
00:38:30,349 --> 00:38:31,225
Maaf.

587
00:38:31,309 --> 00:38:33,102
- Kamu kenapa?
- Kenapa datang?

588
00:38:33,185 --> 00:38:34,186
Terima kasih.

589
00:38:34,270 --> 00:38:36,022
Sama-sama.

590
00:38:36,105 --> 00:38:36,939
Betul!

591
00:38:37,023 --> 00:38:38,566
Saya sangat pelupa!

592
00:38:38,649 --> 00:38:41,569
Saya patut pelawa awak
ara <i>cheong</i> organik saya.

593
00:38:41,652 --> 00:38:42,570
Tak apa.

594
00:38:42,653 --> 00:38:43,904
- Datang lagi.
- Ayuh.

595
00:38:43,988 --> 00:38:45,281
Awak patut pulang.

596
00:38:45,364 --> 00:38:46,949
- Ambil ara…
- Masuk!

597
00:38:47,033 --> 00:38:48,075
- Kejap.
- Ara…

598
00:38:49,368 --> 00:38:50,786
Kenapa dengannya?

599
00:38:56,417 --> 00:38:58,502
Awak ada cerita tentang hari itu?

600
00:38:58,586 --> 00:38:59,879
Awak tak perlu risau.

601
00:38:59,962 --> 00:39:02,381
Saya tak sebut tentang penipuan kerja.

602
00:39:02,465 --> 00:39:03,507
Leganya.

603
00:39:04,675 --> 00:39:08,262
Saya masih cuba baiki keadaan,
jadi dia tak tahu.

604
00:39:08,346 --> 00:39:10,181
Itu urusan awak, bukan saya.

605
00:39:10,765 --> 00:39:11,682
Ya.

606
00:39:26,572 --> 00:39:28,074
Ada sesuatu di muka saya?

607
00:39:30,284 --> 00:39:32,953
Ya, awak nampak macam
orang lahir tahun 1996.

608
00:39:33,788 --> 00:39:34,997
Bagaimana awak tahu?

609
00:39:41,629 --> 00:39:42,588
Macam kenal.

610
00:39:45,174 --> 00:39:46,759
Bukankah itu Mi-jin?

611
00:39:47,718 --> 00:39:48,886
- Hak-chan.
- Apa?

612
00:39:49,470 --> 00:39:51,972
Mi-jin bersama seorang lelaki di sana.

613
00:39:52,056 --> 00:39:53,015
Lelaki?

614
00:39:53,099 --> 00:39:54,558
Lelaki itu!

615
00:39:55,643 --> 00:39:57,269
Awak nak ke mana? Awak gila?

616
00:39:57,353 --> 00:39:58,729
Semuanya baik!

617
00:39:58,813 --> 00:40:01,065
Awak nak hancurkan kehidupan cinta dia?

618
00:40:01,148 --> 00:40:02,525
Tak, cuma…

619
00:40:03,109 --> 00:40:05,027
Tak pernah nampak dia dengan lelaki.

620
00:40:05,569 --> 00:40:06,404
Aduhai.

621
00:40:08,656 --> 00:40:11,492
Dokumen kita tertukar,
saya nak balik dokumen saya.

622
00:40:11,575 --> 00:40:13,035
Begitu. Tertukar.

623
00:40:13,702 --> 00:40:16,539
- Awak tak periksa?
- Ini tak penting buat saya.

624
00:40:17,289 --> 00:40:19,834
Saya boleh bawa jika awak telefon dulu.

625
00:40:19,917 --> 00:40:20,793
Tunggu.

626
00:40:20,876 --> 00:40:22,628
Awak pura-pura tak ingat?

627
00:40:23,212 --> 00:40:25,506
Semasa saya telefon, awak memaki saya.

628
00:40:25,589 --> 00:40:26,841
Betapa sakitnya…

629
00:40:28,384 --> 00:40:29,510
Benarkah?

630
00:40:31,178 --> 00:40:32,847
Tolonglah. Tak mungkin.

631
00:40:32,930 --> 00:40:34,974
Apa? Wah!

632
00:40:35,474 --> 00:40:37,017
Saya telefon awak 27 kali lagi.

633
00:40:37,101 --> 00:40:40,020
Tapi awak tak angkat,
jadi mungkin saya disekat.

634
00:40:40,104 --> 00:40:42,314
Tentu awak salah nombor.

635
00:40:42,398 --> 00:40:43,399
Salah nombor?

636
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:49,071
Lihat.

637
00:40:50,614 --> 00:40:51,907
Itu nombor saya.

638
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:54,493
<i>Sila tinggalkan pesanan.</i>

639
00:40:54,577 --> 00:40:55,494
Ia berdering?

640
00:40:56,370 --> 00:40:57,872
Kenapa awak disekat?

641
00:40:58,747 --> 00:41:00,499
<i>Awak lagi? Pendakwa?</i>

642
00:41:01,167 --> 00:41:04,503
Gila psiko!
Awak siapa telefon saya balik begini?

643
00:41:09,467 --> 00:41:11,218
- Saya boleh jelaskan.
- Lupakan.

644
00:41:11,302 --> 00:41:12,470
Beri dokumen saya.

645
00:41:13,971 --> 00:41:15,973
Saya akan balik dan cari.

646
00:41:16,056 --> 00:41:18,517
Awak nak minum teh kuins dan tunggu?

647
00:41:18,601 --> 00:41:20,519
Tak. Nanti kita dua susah.

648
00:41:20,603 --> 00:41:21,520
Saya tunggu luar.

649
00:41:21,604 --> 00:41:24,190
Saya tinggal berdekatan.

650
00:41:24,773 --> 00:41:25,858
Ke kanan…

651
00:41:25,941 --> 00:41:27,610
Maksud saya, ke kiri sana.

652
00:41:28,194 --> 00:41:29,570
Lihat dia.

653
00:41:29,653 --> 00:41:31,113
Dia tunjuk jalan.

654
00:41:31,197 --> 00:41:32,031
Lihat!

655
00:41:32,114 --> 00:41:33,782
- Tunggu.
- Mereka ke mana?

656
00:41:33,866 --> 00:41:35,743
Dia tunjuk jalan. Ia dah berakhir.

657
00:42:02,186 --> 00:42:03,562
Saya letak di sini?

658
00:42:06,690 --> 00:42:08,734
Tentu saya dah buang semuanya.

659
00:42:13,572 --> 00:42:14,657
Habislah.

660
00:42:31,215 --> 00:42:32,132
Ada kemungkinan

661
00:42:32,967 --> 00:42:34,677
dokumen itu penting?

662
00:42:36,053 --> 00:42:36,887
Ya.

663
00:42:39,765 --> 00:42:41,684
Masalahnya…

664
00:42:42,434 --> 00:42:44,103
Dokumen itu…

665
00:42:45,938 --> 00:42:47,856
Apa yang terjadi sebenarnya…

666
00:42:55,406 --> 00:42:58,158
Awak bakar dokumen saya tanpa kebenaran?

667
00:42:58,242 --> 00:43:00,077
Saya tak tahu itu dokumen awak.

668
00:43:02,121 --> 00:43:03,205
Maafkan saya.

669
00:43:03,289 --> 00:43:06,750
Selepas membuang masa, tenaga
dan emosi saya, awak minta maaf…

670
00:43:06,834 --> 00:43:08,669
Awak fikir "maaf" boleh baikinya?

671
00:43:12,881 --> 00:43:15,134
Ia bukan dokumen kerja awak, bukan?

672
00:43:15,217 --> 00:43:17,720
Kalau bukan pun, ia tak patut dibakar.

673
00:43:18,596 --> 00:43:22,016
Malangnya, ia sangat relevan
dengan kerja saya. Jadi?

674
00:43:24,643 --> 00:43:28,022
Jika kau sanggup berikan hujan,
kenapa tak berikan aku kerja?

675
00:43:30,274 --> 00:43:32,526
Kamu boleh dapat duit dengan menjualnya!

676
00:43:33,736 --> 00:43:37,197
Saya janji akan buat apa saja
untuk tebus kesalahan saya.

677
00:43:39,491 --> 00:43:40,326
Lupakannya.

678
00:43:40,409 --> 00:43:41,368
Tak, tunggu.

679
00:43:42,077 --> 00:43:43,662
Biar saya betulkannya.

680
00:43:44,788 --> 00:43:46,540
Tidak. Jangan buang masa awak.

681
00:43:46,624 --> 00:43:49,501
Ini salah saya.
Saya akan bertanggungjawab.

682
00:43:51,045 --> 00:43:53,047
Awak tak layak cakap begitu.

683
00:43:55,257 --> 00:43:58,218
Sebab si dungu yang kena tipu
tak boleh dipercayai?

684
00:44:00,054 --> 00:44:01,013
Isu rendah diri.

685
00:44:02,556 --> 00:44:03,390
Mari pergi.

686
00:44:03,807 --> 00:44:06,477
Saya akan cari dan berikannya
di depan mata awak.

687
00:44:07,311 --> 00:44:08,312
Ikut saya.

688
00:44:11,732 --> 00:44:12,816
Helo.

689
00:44:12,900 --> 00:44:13,901
Hai.

690
00:44:14,860 --> 00:44:17,488
Saya rasa saya tertinggal
sesuatu hari itu.

691
00:44:17,571 --> 00:44:19,490
- Boleh saya mencarinya?
- Ya.

692
00:44:23,160 --> 00:44:25,704
Awak takkan cari di sini, bukan?

693
00:44:28,040 --> 00:44:30,292
Usah risau. Walaupun tak nampak begitu,

694
00:44:30,376 --> 00:44:33,295
tapi saya ada skor tertinggi
di permainan pencarian di arked.

695
00:44:34,004 --> 00:44:35,172
Tak, awak nampak begitu.

696
00:44:36,423 --> 00:44:37,424
Terima kasih.

697
00:44:38,759 --> 00:44:39,927
Kenapa tak cari?

698
00:44:41,011 --> 00:44:42,012
Saya nak carilah.

699
00:45:10,666 --> 00:45:12,584
Ke mana perginya?

700
00:45:15,462 --> 00:45:16,755
Di mana dokumen itu?

701
00:45:17,798 --> 00:45:18,715
Wah, lihat ini.

702
00:45:19,299 --> 00:45:20,843
Rasanya di sini.

703
00:45:28,642 --> 00:45:33,313
"Buku Pengajian."

704
00:45:38,318 --> 00:45:39,445
Saya hampir mencarut.

705
00:45:43,490 --> 00:45:45,451
"Penjawat awam." Bukan di sini.

706
00:45:52,040 --> 00:45:53,083
Awak tak apa-apa?

707
00:45:53,167 --> 00:45:54,168
Ya.

708
00:46:01,592 --> 00:46:02,593
"Penjawat awam".

709
00:46:12,811 --> 00:46:16,315
Mana Mi-jin? Apa dia sedang buat?

710
00:46:16,398 --> 00:46:17,357
Kenapa belum balik?

711
00:46:17,441 --> 00:46:18,817
Aduhai.

712
00:46:20,569 --> 00:46:22,696
Apa ini? Mereka sedang berseronok.

713
00:46:23,655 --> 00:46:25,782
Anak awak keluar dengan lelaki asing.

714
00:46:25,866 --> 00:46:28,202
Dah lewat dan dia tak balik.
Awak tak risau?

715
00:46:28,285 --> 00:46:30,746
Saya risau jika dia pulang!

716
00:46:30,829 --> 00:46:32,247
Usianya 30 tahun.

717
00:46:32,331 --> 00:46:34,374
Dia tak pernah pegang tangan lelaki.

718
00:46:34,458 --> 00:46:36,460
Nanti kalau dia berakhir jadi

719
00:46:36,543 --> 00:46:39,129
anak dara berusia 60 tahun

720
00:46:39,213 --> 00:46:41,298
yang menjaga orang tuanya,
baru awak sedar?

721
00:46:41,381 --> 00:46:42,925
Kenapa cakap begitu?

722
00:46:47,054 --> 00:46:48,430
Maksud saya…

723
00:46:48,514 --> 00:46:50,682
Seronok juga ada cucu.

724
00:46:50,766 --> 00:46:51,808
Malam ini malamnya.

725
00:46:54,770 --> 00:46:56,730
Malam kita dapat cucu.

726
00:47:00,609 --> 00:47:01,443
Jangan melebih.

727
00:47:03,028 --> 00:47:04,821
Jadi normal. Buat macam biasa.

728
00:47:19,670 --> 00:47:21,171
Awak dah cari di situ.

729
00:47:22,005 --> 00:47:24,174
Banyak buku membuatkan saya keliru.

730
00:47:25,842 --> 00:47:29,304
Jika tak nak tolong, tak perlu membebel.

731
00:47:33,767 --> 00:47:35,811
Awak dah cari di situ 19 minit lalu.

732
00:47:37,062 --> 00:47:39,022
Sebab itu saya cari di sebelah.

733
00:47:39,106 --> 00:47:40,816
- Di situ pun dah.
- Saya tahu.

734
00:47:40,899 --> 00:47:42,401
Saya cari di sebelahnya.

735
00:47:42,484 --> 00:47:44,069
Ya, awak dah cari di situ.

736
00:47:44,152 --> 00:47:46,572
Maksud saya rak ini
yang bersebelahan dengan itu.

737
00:47:49,324 --> 00:47:50,867
Persediaan perkhidmatan awam?

738
00:47:51,618 --> 00:47:52,869
Tunggu sebentar.

739
00:47:54,079 --> 00:47:54,913
Perkhidmatan…

740
00:48:09,011 --> 00:48:10,470
- Awak okey?
- Awak okey?

741
00:49:37,307 --> 00:49:38,433
Kenapa panas sangat?

742
00:49:39,893 --> 00:49:40,936
Awak panas?

743
00:49:43,105 --> 00:49:45,899
Pemilik buka pemanas?

744
00:49:45,982 --> 00:49:47,734
Kenapa panas hari ini?

745
00:49:49,945 --> 00:49:51,154
Kenapa lengan ini?

746
00:49:56,034 --> 00:49:56,993
Cuba ini.

747
00:50:03,041 --> 00:50:04,042
Elok.

748
00:51:52,359 --> 00:51:54,486
LEE MI-JIN
PENTADBIRAN AWAM MODEN

749
00:51:58,532 --> 00:52:00,033
{\an8}KAU BOLEH, MI-JIN

750
00:52:05,622 --> 00:52:08,208
Awak tentu belajar bersungguh-sungguh
untuk ujian.

751
00:52:10,210 --> 00:52:11,378
Itu saja saya lakukan.

752
00:52:11,962 --> 00:52:13,672
Saya terlampau rajin.

753
00:52:14,297 --> 00:52:16,007
Tapi setiap kalinya saya gagal.

754
00:52:17,634 --> 00:52:19,594
Tapi kenapa ambil lagi ujian?

755
00:52:19,678 --> 00:52:21,805
Saya tiada impian.

756
00:52:21,888 --> 00:52:23,598
Saya tiada bakat.

757
00:52:23,682 --> 00:52:26,810
Mak saya nak saya jadi penjawat awam,
jadi saya cuba.

758
00:52:31,606 --> 00:52:34,734
Saya nampak menyedihkan
bagi awak yang bagus dalam segalanya.

759
00:52:34,818 --> 00:52:35,694
Tak, saya cemburu.

760
00:52:37,070 --> 00:52:39,281
Saya pun nak hidup
tanpa tujuan atau pemikiran.

761
00:52:42,033 --> 00:52:45,203
Awak pandai hina orang secara halus.

762
00:52:48,415 --> 00:52:49,416
Awak tengok apa?

763
00:52:50,584 --> 00:52:51,877
Ini.

764
00:52:55,088 --> 00:52:58,216
- Mana awak jumpa ini?
- Rak 15, seksyen tiga.

765
00:52:58,300 --> 00:52:59,551
Di sana.

766
00:52:59,634 --> 00:53:00,760
- Ya.
- Seksyen tiga…

767
00:53:02,596 --> 00:53:03,597
Ini dia!

768
00:53:04,222 --> 00:53:06,141
- Di sini!
- Di sebelah itu.

769
00:53:06,683 --> 00:53:08,852
Tak, di sini. Tunggu sebentar.

770
00:53:09,853 --> 00:53:10,854
Nah.

771
00:53:13,148 --> 00:53:14,274
Helo, Detektif Kwon.

772
00:53:16,151 --> 00:53:17,152
Apa?

773
00:53:19,279 --> 00:53:20,530
Ini dia! Tunggu.

774
00:53:24,117 --> 00:53:25,201
Saya dah jumpa!

775
00:53:26,953 --> 00:53:29,915
Saya ingatkan saya takkan jumpa!

776
00:53:35,378 --> 00:53:36,379
En. Gye?

777
00:53:39,090 --> 00:53:40,091
Apa?

778
00:53:40,550 --> 00:53:42,469
Gaya dia macam nak memerhati semalama<i>n.</i>

779
00:54:04,824 --> 00:54:07,661
<i>Mak!</i>

780
00:54:08,620 --> 00:54:10,330
- Apa yang berlaku?
- Aduhai.

781
00:54:10,413 --> 00:54:11,289
Sekali lagi?

782
00:54:18,713 --> 00:54:21,800
<i>Mak!</i>

783
00:54:25,553 --> 00:54:29,808
Awak suruh saya telefon
jika kami jumpa mayat yang dipotong.

784
00:54:30,433 --> 00:54:32,143
Saya ingat itu.

785
00:54:32,227 --> 00:54:35,271
Siapa sangka ia benar-benar berlaku?

786
00:54:36,564 --> 00:54:37,440
Hei!

787
00:54:37,941 --> 00:54:38,942
Mari sini.

788
00:54:41,194 --> 00:54:43,446
Siapa dia? Awak telefon dia?

789
00:54:43,530 --> 00:54:45,156
Saya bukan nak curi kes.

790
00:54:45,699 --> 00:54:47,575
Nanti kami dapat kes. Saya nak periksa.

791
00:54:47,659 --> 00:54:48,827
Periksa apa?

792
00:54:48,910 --> 00:54:50,954
Untuk lihat jika kami buat kerja?

793
00:54:51,037 --> 00:54:52,747
Jangan begini, tuan.

794
00:54:52,831 --> 00:54:55,458
Saya telefon dia.
Lagipun dia bekerja untuk kes ini.

795
00:54:55,542 --> 00:54:56,835
Lupakannya.

796
00:54:56,918 --> 00:54:58,461
Samseng.

797
00:54:58,545 --> 00:55:00,755
Periksa cepat dan pergi.

798
00:55:01,506 --> 00:55:03,591
Bila mayat ini ditemui?

799
00:55:04,175 --> 00:55:05,635
Ada lelaki tua mahu bersihkan

800
00:55:06,469 --> 00:55:07,554
fros dari rumah hijau.

801
00:55:07,637 --> 00:55:10,682
Dia datang bekerja sebelum subuh
semasa dia jumpa ini.

802
00:55:10,765 --> 00:55:12,267
Bedebah tak guna itu

803
00:55:12,350 --> 00:55:14,769
tinggalkan anggota badan
agar semua orang nampak.

804
00:56:31,930 --> 00:56:34,057
Kenapa dia tak datang balik?

805
00:56:34,140 --> 00:56:35,725
Akhirnya jumpa pun.

806
00:56:40,814 --> 00:56:41,940
Patutkah saya pulang?

807
00:56:43,316 --> 00:56:45,527
Saya boleh saja beri kepadanya esok.

808
00:56:48,404 --> 00:56:52,408
KAMI BELI DAN JUAL BUKU TERPAKAI

809
00:57:11,970 --> 00:57:15,348
<i>Awak tak beredar sebab awak marah, bukan?</i>

810
00:57:15,849 --> 00:57:18,268
Adakah ini terlalu lembut?

811
00:57:18,893 --> 00:57:19,811
<i>Apa yang jadi?</i>

812
00:57:19,894 --> 00:57:21,896
<i>Gaya awak macam nak memerhati semalaman.</i>

813
00:57:21,980 --> 00:57:24,357
Adakah ini terlalu agresif?

814
00:57:27,193 --> 00:57:31,114
Ia perlu kedengaran formal dan tak mesra,

815
00:57:32,198 --> 00:57:35,618
tapi tak boleh kedengaran membosankan.

816
00:57:36,953 --> 00:57:40,165
Mesejnya kenalah menarik
dan kedengaran agak mesra.

817
00:57:41,458 --> 00:57:43,918
Mesej yang sangat menarik.

818
00:57:45,295 --> 00:57:47,589
<i>Saya tunggu, tapi dah lewat.</i>
<i>Jadi saya balik.</i>

819
00:57:49,757 --> 00:57:50,758
Sangat menarik.

820
00:58:34,719 --> 00:58:37,597
<i>Untuk orang dewasa meliputi 550 meter</i>
<i>paling lama 15 minit.</i>

821
00:58:39,265 --> 00:58:41,643
<i>Memandangkan tanah belum kering,</i>

822
00:58:41,726 --> 00:58:43,603
<i>tak sampai 30 minit lagi.</i>

823
00:58:45,772 --> 00:58:47,106
- Detektif Kwon!
- Ya?

824
00:58:47,190 --> 00:58:48,733
Saksi tak nampak sesiapa?

825
00:58:48,816 --> 00:58:50,276
Pembunuh itu mungkin dah lari!

826
00:58:52,237 --> 00:58:54,906
<i>Pembunuh itu terkejut</i>
<i>atau gelabah dengan sesuatu.</i>

827
00:58:58,201 --> 00:59:00,370
Lihat di sana!

828
00:59:02,413 --> 00:59:03,456
<i>Atau mereka sembunyi.</i>

829
00:59:04,707 --> 00:59:06,376
<i>Mungkin untuk betulkan kesilapan?</i>

830
00:59:07,835 --> 00:59:09,546
<i>Pelakunya mungkin masih di sini.</i>

831
00:59:41,869 --> 00:59:42,829
Aduhai.

832
01:00:13,610 --> 01:00:14,611
Detektif Kwon!

833
01:00:14,694 --> 01:00:16,779
Halang semua kenderaan menuju ke Daeho-ri!

834
01:00:16,863 --> 01:00:17,739
Itu pelakunya!

835
01:00:26,372 --> 01:00:28,666
<i>Saya tunggu, tapi dah lewat.</i>
<i>Jadi saya balik.</i>

836
01:00:29,167 --> 01:00:30,835
PERSIMPANGAN DAEHO

837
01:00:30,918 --> 01:00:32,587
<i>Tunggu, itu…</i>

838
01:00:36,591 --> 01:00:38,384
<i>- Nombor anda dail…</i>
- Tolonglah!

839
01:02:29,704 --> 01:02:33,291
Entah apa di dalam ini.
Dia suruh saya berusaha untuk dapatkannya.

840
01:02:33,374 --> 01:02:34,542
Tapi dia tak ambil.

841
01:03:06,783 --> 01:03:08,075
Apa ini?

842
01:03:12,789 --> 01:03:15,917
{\an8}KES KEHILANGAN BERSIRI DI BANDAR SEOHAN

843
01:03:16,000 --> 01:03:18,085
"Kes kehilangan bersiri"?

844
01:03:20,546 --> 01:03:22,256
BUTIRAN PERIBADI ORANG HILANG

845
01:03:45,279 --> 01:03:46,906
{\an8}DAEHO-RI 1.3 KM

846
01:03:59,168 --> 01:04:00,253
Cik Lee Mi-jin!

847
01:04:43,254 --> 01:04:46,173
MISS NIGHT AND DAY

848
01:04:47,174 --> 01:04:48,259
<i>Tapi siapa dia?</i>

849
01:04:50,177 --> 01:04:51,554
{\an8}<i>Ada perkara mencurigakan?</i>

850
01:04:51,637 --> 01:04:52,930
{\an8}<i>Ini penting. Bukan?</i>

851
01:04:53,014 --> 01:04:54,557
{\an8}<i>Masuk dan cakap dengan senyap.</i>

852
01:04:55,516 --> 01:04:57,268
{\an8}Saya tak dengar perbualan mereka.

853
01:04:57,351 --> 01:04:59,186
{\an8}Saya Lee Mi-jin.

854
01:04:59,270 --> 01:05:01,022
{\an8}Ini penipuan panggilan?

855
01:05:02,148 --> 01:05:04,525
{\an8}<i>Mangsa mungkin masih hidup.</i>

856
01:05:05,234 --> 01:05:08,863
{\an8}<i>Dengan pengalaman, keazaman</i>
<i>dan semangat yang melimpah-ruah,</i>

857
01:05:09,655 --> 01:05:11,407
{\an8}<i>En. Lim orang yang sesuai.</i>

858
01:05:11,490 --> 01:05:13,534
{\an8}Saya akan berusaha menyokong awak.

859
01:05:17,038 --> 01:05:22,043
